## Research Notes
- Google Ads API: Python client library `google-ads`. Requires Dev Token, OAuth2 credentials. Workflow: Budget -> Campaign -> AdGroup -> Assets. V23.1.0 is current.
- AI Lead Magnets: Moving to interactive assets. Personalized AI Audits (SEO, ROI), Micro-tools (Humanizers, Generators), and Lead-Generating Agents are top for 2026.
- Ad Asset Creation: Open-source models (LLaMA 3/4, Mistral) used for high-velocity copy. Tools like AgentWeb and Ad Legends for automation.
- Account Warming/Anti-ban: 4-week warming schedule. Start with foundations ($50-100/day), then data accumulation, then gradual scaling (20% increase every 3 days). Use residential proxies (Oxylabs, IPRoyal) and anti-detect browsers.

